    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to people or corporate bodies who own or run manufacturing plants for making automobiles, which are self-propelled vehicles designed primarily to transport passengers over ordinary roads.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
